#### Database Schema Updates
```sql
ALTER TABLE Users ADD COLUMN StripeCustomerId VARCHAR(255);
ALTER TABLE Users ADD COLUMN StripeSubscriptionId VARCHAR(255);
ALTER TABLE Users ADD COLUMN SubscriptionStatus VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'active'; -- active, past_due, canceled, incomplete
ALTER TABLE Users ADD COLUMN SubscriptionPeriodEnd TIMESTAMP;
ALTER TABLE Users ADD COLUMN CancelAtPeriodEnd BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE;
```

#### API Endpoints
```
GET /api/subscriptions/plans
    Response: [{id, name, price, interval, features}]

POST /api/subscriptions/checkout
    Body: { planId, discountCode? }
    Response: { sessionUrl }

GET /api/subscriptions/portal-link
    Response: { url }

POST /api/webhooks/stripe
    Body: Stripe Event Object
    Headers: Stripe-Signature
```

